184
00:14:21,020 --> 00:14:23,130
Půjdu.

185
00:14:27,950 --> 00:14:30,150
-Už jdou.
-Přestaň se dívat.

186
00:14:38,370 --> 00:14:39,930
Yun Duo.

187
00:14:58,710 --> 00:15:04,660
